樜字的基本解释

樜
zhè
古同“柘”。

樜字的汉语字典释义

[①]［zhè］
［《廣韻》之夜切，去禡，章。］
亦作“樜1”。
(1)木名。桑科。落叶灌木或小乔木，叶子卵形或椭圆形，头状花序，果实球形。叶可喂蚕，木质密致坚韧，是贵重的木料，木汁能染赤黄色。
(2)指柘叶。
(3)唐教坊舞曲《柘枝舞》的省称。
(4)通“蔗”。甘蔗。参见“柘漿”。
(5)姓。春秋有越大夫柘稽。见《史记·越王勾践世家》。

樜字的康熙字典解释

【辰集中】【木字部】　樜； 康熙笔画：15； 页码：页550第17
【唐韻】【集韻】【韻會】?同柘。詳柘字註。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［zhè］
["Guangyun" night cut, go to 禡, chapter. ]
Also known as "樜1".
(1) Wooden name. Sankoh. Deciduous shrubs or small trees, oval or elliptical leaves, flower heads, and spherical fruits. The leaves can be fed to silkworms. The wood is dense and tough. It is a precious wood. The wood juice can be dyed reddish yellow.
(2) Refers to Zhe Ye.
(3) The provincial name of Tang Jiaofang dance "Zhezhi Dance".
(4) Through "cane". sugar cane. See "Zhejiang".
(5) Last name. In the Spring and Autumn Period, there will be more and more prosperous people. See "Historical Records · Yue Wang Goujian Family".
